{
  "stem": "352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were in a little city in, in Russia where my dad also, also lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "All I know that I was happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There was a house there, a room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, and I started going to school, I think the first grade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I, I started to learn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then all of sudden, one morning-- this was in 1941-- I don't remember too good what was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I know that my dad was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We met each-- I mean, and my mom was with us and my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My sister said she's going to a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And she was teaching me a little bit Russian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then, one day, there was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we heard explosions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And this must have been June, 1941, when the Russian invaded, and they also invaded the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And my sister said, all I saw that we start packing things again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they said, we have to run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Germans occupied Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they starting to bomb Kiev.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were bombing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I heard explosions, so they were bombing already the little city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because it was close to, to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we started again running again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I remember that we just grabbed a few things, because the city was being bombarded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we went with the other hundreds and thousands of refugees that were going eastward, and because the Ru-- the, the German army was advancing very fast.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I remember, we were huddling in the, in the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I remember my mother was holding me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And my, my sister was next to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And my dad and my mom were sitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they were bombing the places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And then I remember for weeks, we were in a train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And people were running out for hot water.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
